Roger Keith Modder 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President, and Chief Operating Officer at VIRTUSA CORP, Roger Keith Modder  made $1,739,750 in total compensation.  Of this total $256,858 was received as a salary, $92,500 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $1,301,018 was awarded as stock and $89,374 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


