Last Updated: 04/04/2017 



Executive Summary
Modder is Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer with Virtusa Corporation, a global information technology (IT) services company providing IT consulting, technology and outsourcing services. Modder has been with the Westborough, Massachusetts-based firm since 2001. Prior to his promotion to COO in 2011, he  
Personal Attributes and Interests

In a February 2014 article, Forbes Asia observed that Virtusa is Sri Lanka's largest employer in the IT sector and the largest tenant in Colombo's Orion City IT Park, with 150,000 square feet, on the edge of the city. &quot 
